## Anti-Sandbag Gates

- ❌ Do NOT hardcode spy_price. Fetch it live from yfinance.
- ❌ Do NOT hardcode call_wall. Fetch it from StockgridClient.
- ❌ Do NOT skip the `invalidate_signals()` function. Signals MUST flip to invalidated.
- ❌ Do NOT use `print()` for logging. Use `logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)`.
- ❌ Do NOT create frontend files. Python only.
- ❌ Do NOT write "TODO" or "placeholder" anywhere.
- ✅ If yfinance fails (market closed), set `market_open: false` and skip thesis check. Don't crash.
- ✅ If StockgridClient fails (rate limit), use cached wall from morning brief. Don't crash.
- ✅ The snapshot file MUST contain ALL fields from the schema above. Missing fields = FAIL.

